column13: ((11, NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "099360F34898D92C7BA7608FE18DAC34", "That gets me mad")),(9, NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "564D375B42CCB9ABFE4F45BAF2FED5D9", "I\'ll just ignore them")))

column4: NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "1B86101F4DF83BE43523B6913B9F5F72", "Ha ha ha, he\'s bluffing. I won\'t deal with kids.")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "E695FDD8450FB4C005C3FF88B969AAB1", "My master is calling me. Come with me. Ribbit.")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "92E9DED44C28E153B1BDBDA72D7FB225", "{Player} and {Partner}, right? Thanks for coming to Volume Villa!")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "316EFA0249849B77680707B3651F0BE7", "I\'m sorry for what we did to Otamamon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "3F5EA6464A193CE372E5A7AB357456F5", "I\'m grateful. I heard that you\'ve been working hard to save this island.")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "44D5146349559970CD42ABB0BE0B315A", "I\'ve been wanting to help you. Have you been to Misty Trees just north of here?")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "F855883E4A56E37ECE35709EF10ACFB2", "It\'s always foggy there. It\'ll probably be hard for you to get around.")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "95162E2249E9687A125CD8A1687B0FBA", "But you should meet Cherrymon, who is the forest chief.")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "32D9E8BA41CF704CDE77F0A729BB6201", "Cherrymon? I\'ve never heard of such a Digimon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "CE78922A45727BC2AE5477840B19BB9B", "Cherrymon makes the fog in Misty Trees.")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "66026E4A4122D93B634AD9A96ED72314", "He created fog to protect the forest from danger.")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "ED6E6A2F46C1E681C46798AFB908519E", "I think Cherrymon knows something about the cause of the island\'s trouble.")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "39635479479BB44C60191E94F135FDFD", "It\'s worth going thru the fog to see him.")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "37E9BEE04FE4A05E830BDC95FEE7E0EA", "If we can do something about the fog.")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "96817D6D41D47E6A093DE1A12896F193", "The only one who can get rid of the fog is Cherrymon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "B3F587D843A06F1876A71A84E32AEDA8", "But here\'s a way to get thru. I\'ll put a spell on you.")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "05AE5CE240F7C315B87E6CA469A16303", "You\'ll be able to see the road even in the fog.")
NSLOCTEXT("[414B68DB48FCF751B49E6E89EB35E0F4]", "D7E4CBFD43A1A73241B2DFBB88178F53", "Good. That\'s perfect. Now, go to Misty Trees.")
